org.knime.core.node

Class NodeAndBundleInformation

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.knime.core.node.NodeAndBundleInformation

  • public final class NodeAndBundleInformation
extends Object
    Information object to a node. Contains bundle information and node name. Used in persistor to store extra information.
    Since:
    2.6
    Author:
    Bernd Wiswedel, KNIME.com, Zurich, Switzerland
